<div class="title">Three OTTO interfaces</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>OTTO offers three interfaces: <strong>Direktversand</strong>, <strong>Cooperation</strong>, and <strong>Integration</strong>. All interfaces are supported by plentymarkets.<br>
There is a difference in the order import for the interfaces. When using the <strong>Direktversand</strong> and <strong>Cooperation</strong> interfaces, OTTO transfers individual orders to your plentymarkets system which you can process and ship directly to your end customers.<br>
With the <strong>Integration</strong> interface, your plentymarkets system exchanges one multi-order per day with OTTO. In this case, OTTO ships the ordered items to the end customers.</p>
